title: GTA San Andreas + Crack + Multiplayer.zip
description:
1. install power ISO to load the game image file(do not install if u already have any imageloader software)

2. load the GTA San Andreas image file in a drive

3. install GTA San Andreas 

4. copy and paste the crack file inside the installation folder(C:Program Files (x86)Rockstar GamesGTA San Andreas)

5. install the multiplayer software while installation it will ask for folder location of the game. copy and paste this (C:Program Files (x86)Rockstar GamesGTA San Andreas)

6. open the shortcut on the desktop

7. ENJOY!!!
